#. Tag: para
#: faq.xml:82
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"PgAdmin doesn't show anything for large geometries. The best ways to verify "
"you do have data in your geometry columns are?"
msgstr ""
"PgAdmin zeigt bei großen Geometrien nichts an. Was ist der beste Weg, um zu "
